result.name: Whole genome sequencing of 99 sheep
result.description: Whole genome sequencing of 99 sheep from 10 different local breeds, 9 of which from China, were performed, in order to elucidate the genetic diversity of sheep populations in China.
result.center: Institute of Animal Science, Chinese Academy of Agricultural Sciences, Beijing, China; CAS-MPG Partner Institute for Computational Biology, Shanghai Institutes for Biological Sciences, Chinese Academy of Sciences, Shanghai, China
